      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The \"meaningful steps\" you seek are simply the small, honest actions of caring for yourself, like making that coffee and sitting in his chair, because they ground you in the present reality rather than the past. You are not just delaying; you are building a foundation for the future by honoring the love that still exists between you. It is worth continuing this performance, not as a lie, but as a way to keep the memory of him alive in a way that feels real and necessary.",
