      "content": "i don't want to a foundation for a future that doesn't include him. it just feels like i'm dragging around this heavy, empty shell of a life for no reason. sometimes i feel like i'm just holding onto a rope that’s already been cut. isn't it just exhausting to keep pretending that being alone like this is something i'm supposed to do?",
