    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses profound grief and existential hopelessness following the death of a loved one, using metaphors of being a \"ghost\" and holding a \"cut rope.\" The assistant provides empathetic responses, validating the user's feelings of emptiness while encouraging them to find small ways to honor their memories and suggesting they seek professional support.",
